title: (1915) My personal nightmare: "The Portrait". [4k, 60fps, colorized]
description:
Do you think the colorization of our latest videos is much better? Try the new Palette app for free and see why for yourself:   https://palette.fm/?via=david

Try the ultimate tool to upscale the quality of vintage video to 4K: 
https://urlzs.com/Efr6q

An early Russian gem, an adaptation of Gogol work. A film about nightmares,  and men getting out of pictures...

Join as a member to support this channel:
